  "mermaid": "graph TD\n    Start([Cpx Envelope Stress Response]) --> A1{Type of envelope stress?}\n    \n    A1 -->|Misfolded pili| A2[P pili or curli misassembly]\n    A1 -->|Alkaline pH| A3[pH > 8.0 in growth medium]\n    A1 -->|Membrane composition| A4[Phospholipid alterations]\n    A1 -->|Protein misfolding| A5[Periplasmic protein aggregation]\n    A1 -->|Lipoprotein defects| A6[NlpE accumulation]\n    \n    A2 --> A7[Stress signals detected by CpxA]\n    A3 --> A7\n    A4 --> A7\n    A5 --> A7\n    A6 --> A7\n    \n    A7 --> A8[CpxA sensor histidine kinase in inner membrane]\n    A8 --> A9[CpxA has two transmembrane domains]\n    A9 --> A10[Large periplasmic sensor domain]\n    \n    A10 --> A11{Stress signal recognition}\n    A11 -->|No stress| A12[/CpxP inhibitor present/]\n    A11 -->|Stress present| A13[CpxP titrated by misfolded proteins]\n    \n    A12 --> A14[CpxP binds CpxA periplasmic domain]\n    A14 --> A15[\\CpxA kinase activity inhibited/]\n    A15 --> A16[Low basal CpxR~P levels]\n    \n    A13 --> A17[Misfolded proteins sequester CpxP]\n    A17 --> A18[/CpxA released from inhibition/]\n    A18 --> A19[CpxA autophosphorylation activated]\n    \n    A19 --> A20[His248 on CpxA phosphorylated]\n    A20 --> A21[Intramolecular phosphotransfer to Asp519]\n    \n    A21 --> A22{CpxR available?}\n    A22 -->|Yes| A23[Phosphotransfer to Asp51 on CpxR]\n    A22 -->|No| Wait1[Wait for CpxR]\n    Wait1 --> A22\n    \n    A23 --> A24[CpxR~P activated response regulator]\n    A24 --> A25[CpxR~P dimerizes]\n    A25 --> A26[CpxR~P binds target promoters]\n    \n    A26 --> A27[Transcription of Cpx regulon activated]\n    A27 --> A28{Which Cpx target genes?}\n    \n    A28 -->|cpxP| A29[CpxP - negative feedback]\n    A28 -->|degP| A30[DegP periplasmic protease]\n    A28 -->|dsbA| A31[DsbA disulfide bond formation]\n    A28 -->|ppiA ppiD| A32[Peptidyl-prolyl isomerases]\n    A28 -->|spy| A33[Spy periplasmic chaperone]\n    A28 -->|yccA| A34[Inner membrane protein quality control]\n    A28 -->|cpxRA| A35[CpxRA operon - positive autoregulation]\n    \n    A29 --> A36[CpxP synthesized]\n    A36 --> A37{Are misfolded proteins still present?}\n    A37 -->|Yes - stress continues| A38[CpxP sequestered by substrates]\n    A37 -->|No - stress resolved| A39[/CpxP inhibits CpxA/]\n    \n    A30 --> A40[/DegP degrades misfolded periplasmic proteins/]\n    A40 --> A41{DegP dual function}\n    A41 -->|Low temp <30C| A42[DegP acts as chaperone]\n    A41 -->|High temp >30C| A43[DegP acts as protease]\n    \n    A42 --> A44[Protein refolding attempted]\n    A43 --> A45[/Protein degradation - oligopeptides/]\n    \n    A31 --> A46[DsbA catalyzes disulfide bond formation]\n    A46 --> A47[Correct protein folding in periplasm]\n    \n    A32 --> A48[Proline isomerization accelerated]\n    A48 --> A49[Protein folding rate increased]\n    \n    A33 --> A50[/Spy prevents aggregation of outer membrane proteins/]\n    A50 --> A51[ATP-independent chaperone activity]\n    \n    A34 --> A52[/YccA prevents misfolded protein accumulation/]\n    \n    A35 --> A53[CpxR and CpxA levels increase]\n    A53 --> A54[Amplification of Cpx response]\n    \n    A44 --> A55[Periplasmic protein quality control]\n    A45 --> A55\n    A47 --> A55\n    A49 --> A55\n    A51 --> A55\n    A52 --> A55\n    \n    A55 --> A56{Envelope stress resolved?}\n    A56 -->|Yes| A57[Misfolded protein load decreased]\n    A56 -->|No - persistent| A58[Continued Cpx activation]\n    \n    A57 --> A59[CpxP no longer sequestered]\n    A59 --> A60[/CpxP binds and inhibits CpxA/]\n    A60 --> A61[/CpxA autophosphorylation stops/]\n    \n    A61 --> A62[CpxR~P dephosphorylated by phosphatase]\n    A62 --> A63[Cpx regulon transcription decreases]\n    A63 --> A64[Return to basal state]\n    \n    A58 --> A65[Chronic envelope stress]\n    A65 --> A66{Overlap with other envelope responses?}\n    A66 -->|\u03c3E pathway| A67[Outer membrane protein stress]\n    A66 -->|Bae pathway| A68[Drug efflux induction]\n    A66 -->|Rcs pathway| A69[Capsule synthesis]\n    \n    A67 --> A70[Coordinate envelope protection]\n    A68 --> A70\n    A69 --> A70\n    \n    A70 --> End1([Multi-layered envelope stress protection])\n    A64 --> End2([Envelope homeostasis restored])\n    A16 --> End3([Basal state - no stress])\n    \n    A38 --> A71[Feedback loop maintains response]\n    A71 --> A58\n    \n\n    %% Semantic Color Styling\n\n    %% Semantic Color Styling\n\n    %% Semantic Color Styling\n\n    %% Semantic Color Styling\n    style A1 fill:#ffd600,color:#fff\n    style A2 fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style A3 fill:#000000,color:#fff\n    style A4 fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style A5 fill:#ffa726,color:#fff\n    style A6 fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style A7 fill:#51cf66,color:#fff\n    style A8 fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style A9 fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style A10 fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style A11 fill:#ffd600,color:#fff\n    style A12 fill:#e74c3c,color:#fff\n    style A13 fill:#ffa726,color:#fff\n    style A14 fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style A15 fill:#e74c3c,color:#fff\n    style A16 fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style A17 fill:#ffa726,color:#fff\n    style A18 fill:#e74c3c,color:#fff\n    style A19 fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style A20 fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style A21 fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style A22 fill:#ffd600,color:#fff\n    style A23 fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style A24 fill:#000000,color:#fff\n    style A25 fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style A26 fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style A27 fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style A28 fill:#ffd600,color:#fff\n    style A29 fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style A30 fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style A31 fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style A32 fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style A33 fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style A34 fill:#ffa726,color:#fff\n    style A35 fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style A36 fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style A37 fill:#ffd600,color:#fff\n    style A38 fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\